text: 'Delap (Marshallese: ', Marshallese-English Dictionary - Place Name Index) is an island district in the Marshall Islands. It is located in the east of Majuro Atoll. Along with Uliga and Djarrit it forms what is known as the "Delap-Uliga-Djarrit". ==See also== *Majuro Airfield ==References== Category:Majuro Category:Populated places in the Marshall Islands
title: Delap
